T1  - Does natural resource abundance increase Latin American income inequality?1This paper explores in detail one of the main themes of our larger and ongoing inquiry into the factors affecting Latin American income inequality. The dataset used throughout this paper is available at http://www.personal.anderson.ucla.edu/∼peter.schott/.1
